xxl.core.spatial.spatialBPlusTree

Class SingleLevelwiseOptimizedBulkloader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.spatial.spatialBPlusTree.SingleLevelwiseOptimizedBulkloader<T>

  • public class SingleLevelwiseOptimizedBulkloader<T>
extends Object
    This is a bulk loading class for a BPlusTree. Here we use a similar optimization as in RtreeIterativeBulkloader, since we use z-strings our optimization function is a sum of prefixes of z-strings.
